{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, etsi-its-cam-msgs, etsi-its-cam-ts-msgs, etsi-its-cpm-ts-msgs, etsi-its-denm-msgs, etsi-its-vam-ts-msgs, ros-environment }:
